                <div class="w-3/4">一般社団法人日本狩猟協会</div>
            </div>
            <div class="divider my-2"></div>
            <div class="flex">
                <div class="w-1/4">住所</div>
                <div class="w-3/4">287-0225 千葉県成田市吉岡368-91</div>
            </div>
            <div class="divider my-2"></div>
            <div class="flex">
                <div class="w-1/4">代表理事</div>
                <div class="w-3/4">
                    <a
                        href="https://twitter.com/yunoda_3DCG"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-orange"
                    >
                        yunoda
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="divider my-2"></div>
            <div class="flex">
                <div class="w-1/4">理事</div>
                <div class="w-3/4">
                    <a
